How much money do you need to start a game of Monopoly?
flag: Answer: The maximum number of hotel properties a player can put on a single space depends on the number of players in the game. In standard Monopoly, each player has five hotel spaces, and they can put up to three hotels on any given space. If there are more than three players, players may put up to five hotels on a single space.
